<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> The quantities of products eligible for financial compensation under Article 21(3) (a) of Regulation (EC) No 104/2000 shall be calculated on the basis of quantities that are classified under the marketing standards set out in accordance with Article 2 of that Regulation as being of "Extra" and "A" quality only. </inglise>
